jars.search.core

Class SearchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • jars.search.core.SearchResult

  • public class SearchResult
extends Object
    This class contains the result of a search of resources in a repository of directories.

      • getResourcesByFile

        public List<Resource> getResourcesByFile(File f)
        Results of the search for a given File that was in the reach of the search.
        Parameters:
        file - File to search for in the search results. If no result was found in the search, the method will return no Resources. If the file is null, it will neither give any result.
        Returns:
        Results of the search for the specified File

      • getResources

        public List<Resource> getResources()

        Returns:
        Results of the search
